snippet: The freshman Mikaela Foecke had 19 kills, Amber Rolfzen added 10, and Nebraska won its fourth N.C.A.A. volleyball championship with a three-set sweep of Texas in Omaha.
abstract: Nebraska women's volleyball team defeats Texas to win its fourth NCAA volleyball championship.
lead_paragraph: The freshman Mikaela Foecke had 19 kills, Amber Rolfzen added 10, and Nebraska won its fourth N.C.A.A. volleyball championship with a three-set sweep of Texas in Omaha.
